OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 17 May to Tue 26 May
OL,6,FChangeable and at times rather
OL,7,Funsettled conditions look to dominate
OL,8,Fat first, with low pressure often
OL,9,Fclose by. This means periods of rain
OL,10,For showers, some of which could be
OL,11,Fheavy, for many places, though some
OL,12,Fdrier interludes are also expected. As
OL,13,Fthis period progresses, high pressure
OL,14,Fis likely to begin to build from the
OL,15,Fsouth bringing more in the way of
OL,16,Fsettled weather. Temperatures likely
OL,17,Fcooler than average to begin, but
OL,18,Ftending to recover as the period
OL,19,Fprogresses, perhaps becoming rather
OL,20,Fwarm by the end of the period,
OL,21,Fespecially in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
